::Striker::

Striker walks silently along with Spears, his thoughts heavy. He could tell 
that she was sad, and he was a bit mad at himself for reacting that way. He 
sighs quietly. Why did he doubt that she was a sincere Maximal? He could tell 
she had a good spark, and a good sence of humor. He had yet to see any 
Predacons with that quality. He walks closer to her.

"Hey, when you're out of the CR chamber at the Ark, you want me to give you a 
tour of our base?" he asks, trying to change the subject. He was mad at 
himself for reacting as he did, and hoped that she wasn't mad at him for it.
